==English==
===Etymology===
From the surname of [[w:John Wayne Bobbitt|John Wayne Bobbitt]], whose wife cut off his penis.

===Transitive verb===
'''bobbitt''' ('''bobbitts''', '''bobbitting''', '''bobbitted''')

#(''informal'') To cut off the [[penis]] of (a man).
#:''Watch out, she might bobbitt you as you sleep.''